{"@id": "_:Ndb046e60eadd46cd8a02eb31483ce54b", "@type": "madsrdf:Source", "madsrdf:citationNote": "title page (Gayla Partridge) inside dust jacket (Gayla Partridge is a Texas native with a Fine Arts
